init_text: A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She's unaware that she's actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who's fallen for her, and is certain he's going to get it right this time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They could be anyone, and it was easy to get a date.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The shapeshifter was instantly smitten, and decided to make a move.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The shapeshifter approached the woman, and struck up a conversation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was looking for someone who would treat her right, and be there for her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She would always say that she was not ready for a relationship, and that she wanted to focus on her art.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The shapeshifter was at a loss, and didn't know what else to do.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They would continue to date other people, but they would never feel the same way about anyone else as they did about the artist.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They were all sitting at the bar, talking, when the artist walked in.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They would no longer try to be anyone else, and they would no longer hide their true identity from the artist.
